{"title":"哨所迎春曲（图片）","authors":["甘迎祥","金钟"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨所迎春曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘迎祥画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金钟诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（在法卡山前线，一个弹药库房顶，搭起了和平鸽的鸽舍……）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是童话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是想象的战地浪漫曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法卡山一个哨所的屋顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缭绕着一群鸽子的温馨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，钢筋铁骨的地基，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支撑着和平！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声刚刚响过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友，就在这青山下长眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，和平之子，祖国之子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用钢枪蘸着热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抒写着祖国的神圣。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}